# 🏗️ Crewera Reality — Backend File Structure

> **Node.js + Express + MySQL (Sequelize)** · All 22 Modules · 190+ APIs

---

## 📁 Root Structure

```
D:\CREWERA\backend\
├── 📄 package.json
├── 📄 .env
├── 📄 .env.example
├── 📄 .gitignore
├── 📄 .eslintrc.js
├── 📄 .prettierrc
├── 📄 server.js                          ← Entry point
├── 📄 app.js                             ← Express app setup
│
├── 📁 config/                            ← All configuration
├── 📁 database/                          ← SQL & migrations
├── 📁 src/
│   ├── 📁 models/                        ← Sequelize models (22)
│   ├── 📁 controllers/                   ← Route handlers (18)
│   ├── 📁 routes/                        ← Express routers (18)
│   ├── 📁 middlewares/                   ← Auth, error, upload (6)
│   ├── 📁 services/                      ← Business logic (10)
│   ├── 📁 validators/                    ← Joi schemas (15)
│   ├── 📁 utils/                         ← Helpers & utilities (8)
│   └── 📁 jobs/                          ← Cron & background jobs (4)
│
├── 📁 uploads/                           ← File upload storage
├── 📁 logs/                              ← Application logs
├── 📁 tests/                             ← Test suites
└── 📁 docs/                              ← API documentation
```

---

## 📁 config/

```
config/
├── 📄 database.js                 # MySQL/Sequelize connection config
├── 📄 app.js                      # App-level settings (port, cors, rate limit)
├── 📄 auth.js                     # JWT secret, token expiry, bcrypt rounds
├── 📄 mail.js                     # SMTP / email service config
├── 📄 upload.js                   # Multer config (file size, allowed types, paths)
├── 📄 cloudinary.js               # Cloud storage config (optional)
├── 📄 constants.js                # App-wide enums, defaults, status codes
└── 📄 logger.js                   # Winston logger configuration
```

