## 📁 src/controllers/

```
src/controllers/
├── 📄 auth.controller.js              # Register, login, logout, reset, verify
├── 📄 user.controller.js              # Profile CRUD, preferences, login history
├── 📄 property.controller.js          # Public: list, search, detail, nearby, trending
├── 📄 propertyAdmin.controller.js     # Admin: full CRUD, all sub-tables, status mgmt
├── 📄 pricing.controller.js           # Admin: pricing variants, unit specs CRUD
├── 📄 media.controller.js             # Admin: upload, reorder, delete, set primary
├── 📄 amenity.controller.js           # Admin: amenity master CRUD + property mapping
├── 📄 milestone.controller.js         # Admin: construction milestones CRUD
├── 📄 review.controller.js            # Submit, moderate, helpful, report
├── 📄 lead.controller.js              # Admin: leads pipeline, assign, follow-up
├── 📄 inquiry.controller.js           # Submit, reply, admin list, stats
├── 📄 propertyRequest.controller.js   # Submit, complete, admin review (ROI)
├── 📄 favorite.controller.js          # Add, remove, check, comparisons
├── 📄 blog.controller.js              # Posts CRUD, categories, comments, admin
├── 📄 content.controller.js           # Testimonials, FAQs, contact messages
├── 📄 notification.controller.js      # User notifications + admin broadcast
├── 📄 analytics.controller.js         # Property analytics, market trends, dashboard
├── 📄 audit.controller.js             # Admin: audit logs, activity, security
├── 📄 tag.controller.js               # Admin: tags CRUD + property tag mapping
└── 📄 search.controller.js            # Saved searches, autocomplete, alerts
```

