## 📁 src/middlewares/

```
src/middlewares/
├── 📄 auth.middleware.js              # JWT verification, extract user
├── 📄 role.middleware.js              # Role-based access (admin, agent, user, builder)
├── 📄 validate.middleware.js          # Joi validation runner (req.body/query/params)
├── 📄 upload.middleware.js            # Multer file upload (photo, video, document)
├── 📄 rateLimiter.middleware.js       # Rate limiting per IP/user
├── 📄 error.middleware.js             # Global error handler (structured JSON errors)
├── 📄 audit.middleware.js             # Auto-log actions to audit_logs
└── 📄 cors.middleware.js              # CORS configuration
```

