## 📁 src/validators/

```
src/validators/
├── 📄 auth.validator.js               # Register, login, reset password schemas
├── 📄 user.validator.js               # Profile update, preferences schemas
├── 📄 property.validator.js           # Property create/update (all 8 steps)
