## 📁 Root Files

### `server.js`
```js
// Imports app, connects DB, starts server on process.env.PORT
```

### `app.js`
```js
// Express setup: cors, helmet, morgan, rate-limiter, body-parser
// Mount routes: /api/auth, /api/properties, /api/admin/*, etc.
// Global error handler middleware
```

### `.env.example`
```env
# Server
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=development

# Database
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=3306
DB_NAME=crewera_reality
DB_USER=root
DB_PASSWORD=

# JWT
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN=30d

# Email
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=your_email
SMTP_PASS=your_app_password
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@crewera.com

# Upload
MAX_FILE_SIZE=10485760
UPLOAD_PATH=./uploads

# Cloudinary (optional)
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=

# Frontend
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:3000
```

